{"tid":2078870,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透社︰美國將華為等20間中國企業列為受解放軍控制","createTime":"2020-06-25T11:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T16:42:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e267433f74291300b0557aab9ecf0eae8256f0e","tid":2078870,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uVmUCWs1iyKCA3iznBE1Wg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/a25e2ee0-b6a2-11ea-bf57-28322178c2ef\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuVmUCWs1iyKCA3iznBE1Wg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2Fa25e2ee0-b6a2-11ea-bf57-28322178c2ef&h=a0cff843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，美國政府將20間中國大型企業，列為由中國軍方擁有或控制，當中包括電信設備商華為及視像監控公司海康威視，為美國實施新的金融制裁奠定基礎。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述一份文件披露，被列為由解放軍支持、並在美國營運的公司，還包括中移動、中國電信及中航工業等，總統有權根據法律實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n國防部一名不願意透露姓名的官員，確認這份文件的真實性，又說文件已經送交國會。<br />\n<br />\n美中兩國在技術、貿易和外交政策方面的緊張局勢不斷升級，五角大樓在兩黨議員施壓下，公佈這些中國企業名單。報道說，白宮、中方及相關中國企業都未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/路透社-美國將華為等20間中國企業列為受解放軍控制-011925820.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%AD%8920%E9%96%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%88%97%E7%82%BA%E5%8F%97%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6-011925820.html&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=612da99a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/路透社-美國將華為等20間中國企業列為受解放軍控制-011925820.html</a>"},{"pid":"9c762a69e40301d325f36ad33566ecde72b0622d","tid":2078870,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"［行動po置頂］全民報哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2078606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2078606</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"875e257fa3aa4c9165d2b173db9e3c1bfbd0bf4d","tid":2078870,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9260e4dcfa499840c33964f784493f973144a3","tid":2078870,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd7316fd5146683d17900f764906bc3f258debb","tid":2078870,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"178715f717ad49bce87e7041321721569aad6315","tid":2078870,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T16:30:16.000Z","msg":"咁遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dcc2abcdb440450b0569a633e6dd4bee29ef6a","tid":2078870,"uid":337345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續褶被"}]}